snippet.title: DORAEMON  STORY OF SEASONS –  Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Tend to your crops, go fishing, cook delicious meals, or hang out with Noby's friends. There is so much to do in this whimsical farming adventure! DORAEMON  STORY OF SEASONS is available today for #NintendoSwitch and #PC.
